{"tid":1975264,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【油尖旺區議會討論「重組警隊」議案  民政專員及警方代表即離場】","createTime":"2020-04-16T12:02:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-16T18:10:41.000Z","uid":103653,"like":195,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"03d6f1537cecbd7af1df5e6e02dee96dea5c00ba","tid":1975264,"uid":103653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T12:02:28.000Z","msg":"油尖旺區議會開始討論「重組警隊，停止濫暴」議案時，警方指控有關議案是「仇警」，又指油尖旺區會「食人血饅頭，連決都舔埋」，有區議員大笑回應，並高叫「重組警隊，停止濫暴」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">民政專員余健強及警方代表隨後離場</span>，有區議員追出，並指控民政專員並非政治中立，又指余健強涉嫌公職人員行為失當。<br />\n<br />\n有區議員指，警方作為打人者卻指責議員，其後區議會通過「重組警隊，停止濫暴」議案，但民政專員的離場令議案和會議失去官方紀錄；區議會提出臨時動議，向廉政公署舉報余健強涉嫌公職人員行為失當，並獲通過。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XG6Pw3y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXG6Pw3y.jpg&h=b28e500d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c0a42ee8b1f2cfc7d09abb3200ad409c342e020","tid":1975264,"uid":83251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T12:02:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"962bd5a52dbf41ca6c78e1e713df421bad119112","tid":1975264,"uid":108337,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T12:04:22.000Z","msg":"點解通常都冇人將奶共民政專員起底？"},{"pid":"f939eb6342d59fe4a2525976a52be973ed193440","tid":1975264,"uid":66221,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T12:04:40.000Z","msg":"茹毛飲血去話人食人血饅頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b846d8403e5a48f2f6c3f89902849abf9becf169","tid":1975264,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T12:09:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3756a6225f20fd2b8187c3e1ac58c038e4280557","tid":1975264,"uid":199893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-16T12:10:21.000Z","msg":"推到呢班仆街死"},{"pid":"e0b141edafe2e3bf98e7ec3d9bb77cbe2691631c","tid":1975264,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi